articles.title: Fallout London may be “forced” into launch despite Fallout 4 next gen - PCGamesN
articles.description: Fallout London is a transformative mod that was previously delayed, but the dev says it may be forced to launch despite Fallout 4 next gen.
articles.content: With Starfield DLC and The Elder Scrolls 6 still in the works, Fallout London feels like the closest thing to a genuine Fallout 5 that we could see for a while. A gigantic mod that relocates Bethesda… [+3117 chars]
